		<td class='confluenceTd'> The screen shows an image with no previous description. <br class="atl-forced-newline" />  <span class="image-wrap" style="float: right"><a class="confluence-thumbnail-link 1275x677" href='/images/help/Description_Pane-thumb.png'><img src="/images/help/Description_Pane-thumb.png" width="300" style="border: 1px solid black" /></a></span><br class="atl-forced-newline" /> </td>
