		</td>
		<td class='confluenceTd'> Description fields will be displayed on the right of the image you have selected. &nbsp;The screen below lists all the possible data elements that can be described for a description. <br class="atl-forced-newline" />
		<br class="atl-forced-newline" />  <span class="image-wrap" style="float: right"><a class="confluence-thumbnail-link 946x917" href='/images/help/DescriptionPanel-ContentModel.png'><img src="/images/help/DescriptionPanel-ContentModel-thumb.png" style="border: 1px solid black" /></a></span><br class="atl-forced-newline" /> </td>
